    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway, this is not the point right now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But apparently, they were to-- to this house, to this family, there was a cleaning lady coming.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was cleaning those two ladies' rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, same time, she was cleaning the room where Lilian was living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, she was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] telling those landladies that she is a daughter of wealthy farmer, Polish farmer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was afraid to be grabbed for the forced labor in Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she run away from that place where her parents are living, and she came to Warsaw, and she lives in this room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you understand the environment which was given.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
